headline: Sempra (SRE): Is There More Upside After Recent Momentum? A Fresh Look at Valuation
summary: Sempra (SRE) shares have gained some ground in the past month, up around 4%. Investors are keeping a close eye on its performance because the company’s steady growth continues to shape expectations for the utility sector. See our latest analysis for Sempra. Looking beyond this month’s bump, Sempra’s momentum has really picked up. Its 90-day share price return stands at an impressive 15.85%, and the total shareholder return over the past year is a solid 6.02%. Both short- and long-term signals...
